            <title>[LUCENE-2924] fix getting started / demo docs</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2924</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;Opening a new issue for this since there are a number of problems...:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;We should get the versions right, eg when we explain how to do a src checkout it should point to the path for that release&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Source checkout / build JARs instructions must be updated for the merger&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Analyzers JAR must be on the classpath too&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Demo sources are no longer shipped in a binary release&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fixup from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2923&quot; title=&quot;cleanup contrib/demo&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUCENE-2923&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (remove web app, new command-line ops for IndexFiles, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
